snippet: SEYKORA--Barbara, 85, died April 23, 2016 in Florida. Born in Corona, NY she moved to Miami in 1960 with husband Lawrence and daughters Karen and Dana. Survived by Dana O'Keefe, grandchildren and great-grandchildren, this loving woman will be missed. 1/3
